<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>A.V. Logistics - Consignment Receipt (A4)</title>
    <style>
      /* Page sizing for accurate A4 PDF output */
      @page {
        size: A4;
        margin: 10mm;
      }
      html,
      body {
        height: 297mm; /* A4 height */
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background: white;
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      }

      .sheet {
        width: 210mm; /* A4 width */
        min-height: 297mm;
        padding: 12mm 12mm;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 4mm;
        margin-bottom: 6mm;
      }
      .company-title {
        font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        font-size: 28px;
        color: #c40000;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      /* Top logo area (wing emblem on right) */
      .top-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .logo-right {
        width: 110px;
        height: 40px;
        position: relative;
        margin-right: 6mm;
      }
      /* Simple wing emblem made with CSS */
      .emblem {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }
      .emblem .circle {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 2px solid #222;
        display: inline-block;
        background: #fff;
        position: absolute;
        right: 0;
        top: 2px;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 36px;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .wing {
        position: absolute;
        height: 26px;
        top: 7px;
        left: 0;
        right: 48px;
        border-top: 2px solid #222;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #222;
        border-radius: 50px;
        transform-origin: left center;
        opacity: 0.95;
      }

      /* Outer framed receipt */
      .receipt-wrap {
        border: 3px solid #111;
        padding: 12px;
        margin-top: 6mm;
      }
      .receipt-inner {
        border: 1px solid #111;
        padding: 8px;
      }

      .top-grid {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
      }
      .box {
        flex: 1;
        border: 1px solid #111;
        padding: 8px;
        font-size: 11px;
      }
      .box h4 {
        margin: 0 0 6px 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .note {
        font-size: 10px;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      /* Main details table */
      table.details {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 8px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      table.details td,
      table.details th {
        border: 1px solid #111;
        padding: 6px;
      }
      table.details th {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        text-align: left;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .small-muted {
        font-size: 10px;
        color: #333;
      }

      /* Footer small note */
      .footer-note {
        margin-top: 8px;
        font-size: 11px;
      }

      /* Make sure printing matches on PDF */
      @media print {
        html,
        body {
          width: 210mm;
          height: 297mm;
        }
        .sheet {
          box-shadow: none;
          margin: 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="sheet">
      <div class="header top-row">
        <div></div>
        <div class="company-title">A.V.LOGISTICS</div>
        <div class="logo-right">
          <div class="logo-right">
            <img
              src="https://i.ibb.co/twdQjjK0/av-logo.jpg"
              alt="Company Logo"
              style="width: 100%; height: auto"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="receipt-wrap">
        <div class="receipt-inner">
          <div class="top-grid">
            <div class="box">
              <h4>AT OWNER'S RISK</h4>
              <p class="note">
                <strong>SCHEDULE OF DEMURRAGE CHARGES</strong><br />
                Demurrage chargable after......days from @Rs......per.......day
                per on weight Charged
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="box">
              <h4>CRUTION</h4>
              <p class="note">
                This consignment will not be Detained,diverted re-routed re
                booked without consigne Bank's Written Permission.<br /><small
                  class="small-muted"
                  >NOTE: The consignment coverby this lorry Receipt be stored at
                  the destination under the control of transport operator and
                  will be detined of the order of the consignee bank whose Name
                  Mentioned to the lorry recept it will under no Circumstance be
                  derived to anyone withoutthe authority.</small
                >
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="box">
              <h4>INSURANCE</h4>
              <p class="note">
                The customer has Stated that:<br />—He has not intructed the
                consignment<br />—He has instructed the consignment
                Company......Policy No........Amount.....Risk
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Main table with fields similar to image -->
          <table class="details" style="margin-top: 10px">
            <tr>
              <th style="width: 12%">GR.NO</th>
              <td style="width: 28%"></td>
              <th style="width: 12%">DATE</th>
              <td style="width: 48%"><%=date %> <%=time%></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Truck No.</th>
              <td><%=truckNumber%></td>
              <th>Actual Wt</th>
              <td><%= weight %></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Consignor</th>
              <td></td>
              <th>Packing Mode</th>
              <td>LOOSE</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Consignee</th>
              <td></td>
              <th>Contains</th>
              <td><%= description %></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Invoice No :</th>
              <td></td>
              <th>INV.AMOUNT :</th>
              <td></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>Ewaybill</th>
              <td></td>
              <th>Frt.Amt</th>
              <td style="text-align: right; font-weight: 700"></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <th>For :</th>
              <td colspan="3"></td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <p class="footer-note">
            <strong>Note :</strong> No Responsibility for Leakage &amp; Breakage
            Company Is Not Responsibility For Re Booking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
